      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The highest mount, He can make plain;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The wildest flood, He can restrain!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God of Impossibilities!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Poor puny man, now learn His ways."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The axe did swim on Jordan’s wave!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our God the Red Sea’s waters clave!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He stopped the sun! made long the day!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is the God to whom we pray."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He bars the sea with feeble sand!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The proud waves bow at His command!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If God is thine, what more your need?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Can He not work for you indeed?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our God is love; your needs are known;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His promises He’ll fully own."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our gracious God bows down His ear"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The feeblest, weakest cry to hear."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our God is light, and never yet,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One promise did He e’er forget."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His promises in Christ the Son"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are fully pledged, Yea and Amen."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our faithful God, faith cannot break,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor death, nor hell, His promise shake!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Who ask in faith, He’ll not deny;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His Word is sure, He must reply."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He faileth not, let all men hear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He faileth not, His Word is clear."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He faileth not, His grace how good;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He faileth not, for He is God!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    }
  ],
